response.original_title: MAYBE THERE'S A KINGDOM ABOVE THE WEATHER
response.overview: Denial, anger, bargaining, depression, acceptance. This story follows a nineteen year old boy in therapy as he attempts to overcome and heal from his past trauma with the help of his younger self.
response.tagline: With a little help from myself.
response.title: MAYBE THERE'S A KINGDOM ABOVE THE WEATHER
